    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> soy sauce</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong> and <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further or until the prawns are cooked through</p><p>Note: Please make sure you cook your prawns thoroughly (until piping hot!) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
